                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7498" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0192</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1657 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">明利蔬菜合作社：红色的心，绿色的菜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mingli Vegetable Cooperative: Sincere heart, pollution-free vegetables</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">温凤荣,王洪生（通讯作者）,李金蔓,李天翊,蒲小彤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东农业大学*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东明利特色蔬菜种植专业合作社</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合作社；社会责任；乡村振兴；食品安全；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cooperatives; Social Responsibility; Rural Revitalization;Food Safety</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">发展农业专业合作社是推动乡村产业兴旺、提高农业组织化程度、实现共同富裕的有效途径。济南市莱芜区明利特色蔬菜种植专业合作社（以下简称明利蔬菜合作社）是一家绿色蔬菜的综合运营商，但是合作社自筹建之初便十分重视并以身作则地践行农业企业应承担的社会责任。本案例以明利蔬菜合作社的创立、发展历程为主脉络，讲述创始人创办明利蔬菜合作社的初心以及现任主理人带领团队对企业社会责任不同阶段的摸索、尝试及转变过程。在此过程中，明利蔬菜合作社先后解决了村民抵触、产品定位不明晰、标准化种植落实不到位、带动周边地区脱贫机制不明确等问题。本文以案例形式描述农业专业合作社在履行社会责任的过程中可能面临的困境以及解决方法，同时也诠释了合作社主理人在合作社承担社会责任的过程中发挥的重要作用。为其他农业专业合作社探索如何运用自身资源助力乡村振兴工作，走向共同富裕具有较好的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The development of agricultural cooperatives is an effective way to promote the prosperity of rural industries, improve the organization of agriculture and achieve common prosperity. Mingli Vegetable Cooperative (hereinafter referred to as Mingli Vegetable Cooperative) is a comprehensive operator of green vegetables, but since its establishment, the cooperative has attached great importance to the social responsibility of agricultural enterprises by setting an example. This case focuses on the establishment and development of Ming Lee Vegetable Cooperative, and tells the story of the founder&#39;s initial intention to establish Ming Lee Vegetable Cooperative and the current director&#39;s team&#39;s exploration, experimentation and transformation of corporate social responsibility at different stages. In this process, Mingli Vegetable Cooperative has solved the problems of villagers&#39; resistance, unclear product positioning, lack of standardized planting implementation, and unclear mechanism to drive the surrounding areas out of poverty. This paper describes the dilemmas that agricultural cooperatives may face in the process of fulfilling social responsibility and the solutions in the form of cases, and also explains the important role played by cooperative principals in the process of cooperatives&#39; social responsibility. It is a good reference for other agricultural cooperatives to explore how to use their own resources to help alleviate and help the poor and move toward common prosperity.
As an agricultural cooperative, Mingli Vegetable Cooperative contributes to driving the surrounding areas out of poverty and revitalizing the agricultural industry, and actively responds to the national development trend. By describing the process of Mingli Vegetable Cooperative&#39;s social responsibility at various stages of development, this case aims to guide students to learn and master theories related to social responsibility and provide relevant experience for other agricultural cooperatives to integrate resources and promote rural revitalization.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者理论;战略型企业社会责任;社会责任评估ESG体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
